      <p>Nepal is rich in cultural heritage, with diverse traditions influenced by Hinduism, Buddhism, and local practices. The people of Nepal celebrate numerous festivals like Dashain and Tihar, each with its unique significance.</p>
      <img src="nepal_culture.jpg" alt="Nepali Culture" class="image">
