    <section id="landscape">
      <h2>The Landscape of Nepal</h2>
      <p>From the towering Himalayas to lush valleys and terraced fields, Nepal's landscape is breathtaking. The country is home to Mount Everest, the world's highest peak, and is a haven for trekkers and nature lovers.</p>
      <img src="nepal_landscape.jpg" alt="Nepal Landscape" class="image">
